{"summary":"<p>今天在写一个小Demo时，遇到一个很奇怪的问题，弄了很久最终才勉强解决，问题是这样的，在子类中调用父类的一个属性的方法始终不行，但在父类里面可以调用</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p>如下图所示<br>父类里方法实现<br><a href=\"/resources/2014/10/strange_base.png\"><img src=\"/resources/2014/10/strange_base.png\" alt=\"strange_base\">\n</a>子类里重写这个方法<br><a href=\"/resources/2014/10/strange_problem.png\"><img src=\"/resources/2014/10/strange_problem.png\" alt=\"strange_problem\">\n</a>代码提示中是可以看到有这个方法的<br><a href=\"/resources/2014/10/strange_problem_2.png\"><img src=\"/resources/2014/10/strange_problem_2.png\" alt=\"strange_problem_2\">\n</a>但编译时报错</p>\n<p>[text]<br>incompatible types: LayoutParams cannot be converted to int<br>mTabLayout.addView(tabView, new LinearLayout.LayoutParams(0, MATCH_PARENT, 1));<br>[/text]</p>\n<p>为了获取更详细错误信息，在命令行上执行</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">gradle assembleDebug</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>但提示如下图所示错误<br><a href=\"/resources/2014/10/problem_1.png\"><img src=\"/resources/2014/10/problem_1.png\" alt=\"problem_1\"></a><br>即使修改成</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mTabLayout.addView(tabView);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>也会提示如下错误<br><a href=\"/resources/2014/10/problem_2.png\"><img src=\"/resources/2014/10/problem_2.png\" alt=\"problem_2\"></a></p>\n<p>用反射也不行，直接到这里就报错了</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mTabLayout.getClass().getMethod...</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>最后终于用这种方式可以勉强通过，即<strong>强制类型转换一下</strong><br><a href=\"/resources/2014/10/strange_solve.png\"><img src=\"/resources/2014/10/strange_solve.png\" alt=\"strange_solve\"></a></p>\n<p>其实我在运行时可以执行一下这句，并且没有错误</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mTabLayout.addView(tabView, <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> LinearLayout.LayoutParams(<span class=\"number\">0</span>, MATCH_PARENT, <span class=\"number\">1</span>));</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>"}